asting though so you will have to reapply after a few hours. New colors are all 10/10 pretty. They are on the deeper side so if you prefer lighter shades these might be too dark for you.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGet Happy is a pretty soft rose pink\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDolce Vita is a warm rose\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMake a Move is a muted orange/apricot\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmooth Talk is a transparent taupe\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWhat If is a cool toned brown\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Afterglow Lip Shine Lip Gloss new shades\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Light Reflecting Luminizing Powder + Afterglow Lip Shine (New Shades). Sharing a look at the latest launches from NARS.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/06/nars-light-reflecting-luminizing-powder-afterglow-lip-shine-new-shades.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Light Reflecting Luminizing Powder + Afterglow Lip Shine (New Shades)\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Afterglow-Liphine-Gloss-new-shades-swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://theb