atches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-swatches.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI received Heavenly* at a NARS event in Miami (quick \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@beautylookbook/video/7505935144327384362\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cem\u003epeek here\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e in case you’re curious!) and I purchased the others from \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4eevFbK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eUlta\u003c/a\u003e. I still think Heavenly is the best one, it’s a really stunning pink.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEros is a soft cool toned ivory\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElectra is a light champagne\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOphelia is a golden champagne\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeavenly is a metallic pink\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTotal Eclipse is a warm copper shimmer\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSince the shimmer and glistening effect is on the intense side I don’t know that I can wear these everyday. They do make for a really beautiful special glow, but I prefer the subtle glow of the newer \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/06/new-prada-beauty-launches.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003ePrada Highlighters\u003c/a\u003e. Also I know the \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/01/chanel-spring-summer-2025.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eChanel spring highlighter quad\u003c/a\u003e is sold out, but I am still reaching for that one on a regular basis.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLooks wearing each highlighter with a different lip. For skintone reference I wear the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3ZDfley\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eNARS Light Reflecting Foundation\u003c/a\u003e in either Vanuatu or Barcelona right now and the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/443lmCI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eRadiant Creamy Concealer\u003c/a\u003e in Ginger. (My lighter spring time foundation shade is Sahel).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4eevFbK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eLight Reflecting Luminizing Powder\u003c/a\u003e in Eros + \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/43OQOFY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eAfterglow Liquid Blush\u003c/a\u003e in Dolce Vita + \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4nfSrUW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eAfterglow Lip Shine\u003c/a\u003e in Dolce Vita\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-Eros.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NARS-Light-Reflecting-Luminizing-Powder-Eros-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Light Reflecting Luminizing Powder in Eros\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Light Reflecting Luminizing Powder + Afterglow Lip Shine (New Shades). Sharing a look at the latest launches from NARS.\" data-jp